      "title": "Control of male gametophyte development",
      "abstract": "In a previous review of male gametophyte development ([McCormick, 1993][1]), it was noted that the two areas posed by [Mascarenhas (1975)][2] as fruitful areas for future research were the following. What are the differences in the two cytoplasms that determine the different cell fates of the"
